<HEADLINE> Holdridge Added to Pan Am Team </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	TUCSON, Ariz. (AP) -- David Holdridge, a Seattle Mariners  
farmhand, was added Wednesday to the U.S. roster for the Pan 
American games, July 24-Aug. 2 in Winnipeg. 
</P>
