<HEADLINE> London Shares Close Higher / British Stocks  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LONDON (AP) -- Share prices rose Wednesday on the London Stock  
Exchange. 
</P>
<P>
	The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index was up 27.5  
points, or 0.4 percent, at 6,473.1. 
</P>
<P>
	Provisional volume was 1 billion shares, unchanged from Tuesday.  
  	   	
</P>
